items.name: Hacker-guide-
items.description: When asked if coding knowledge is needed for hacking, the answer is almost always the same: It's possible to become a great hacker without coding knowledge, but having coding experience makes it a whole lot easier. Knowing how software is built in theory makes it easier to break.
